SUMMARY:CHASER (USA) / SNAILMATE (USA) (Uhrzeit prüfen)
LOCATION:Chelsea
DESCRIPTION:CHASER (Melodic Punk Rock / Huntingtown Beach / USA) Comprised of Mike LeDonne (singer)\, Jesse Stopnitzky (bassist/vocals)\, Bill Hockmuth (guitarist) and Davey Guy (drums)\, CHASER shares the same love for punk rock as the rest of us\, hoping to make a difference. Jesse shares\, “Growing up in the 90’s\, no sound has struck a chord for us like the Fat and Epitaph era punk bands. Although the scene continues to evolve\, we stick to what we love most about this genre…catchy melodies\, anthemic choruses\, passionate lyrical content and as always\, a beat that has you rushing for the pit.” https://chaserpunkrock.com/ www.facebook.com/chaserband    SNAILMATE (Phoenix / USA / Synthpunk\, Grindcore Pop and Nerd rap) Snailmate is the Phoenix-based musical duo composed of lyricist\, singer and synth-wizard Kalen Lander and drummer and backup vocalist Bentley Monet. Together\, the two create music that fuses synthpunk\, grindcore pop\, and nerd rap for an unpredictable and explosive sound. The band is known for their frenetic and impressive live shows. Performing over a thousand shows\, Snailmate has cultivated a fervent fanbase that aims to be inclusive with the band priding their shows as a safe space for all genders and people of all sexualities. https://snailmate.com www.facebook.com/snailmate  Tickets: www.oeticket.com/eventseries/mj-presents-chaser-snailmate-4081843/
URL:https://www.chelsea.co.at/concerts.php#concert_6632
